OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe: 'I would rather
OL,4,Csign the next Mbappe than buy success'
OL,6,FSir Jim Ratcliffe has warned against
OL,7,Fthe prospect of trying to land
OL,8,Fsuperstar signings like Jude
OL,9,FBellingham or Kylian Mbappe.
OL,11,FThe Ineos chairman is taking control
OL,12,Fof footballing operations at United
OL,13,Ffollowing his recent minority purchase
OL,14,Fand wants to turn them back into the
OL,15,Fforce they once were.
OL,17,FHowever, he believes spending big on
OL,18,Fmarquee signings is not the way to
OL,19,Fprosper.
