OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe: 'I would rather
OL,4,Csign the next Mbappe than buy success'
OL,6,FAppearing as a guest on Geraint
OL,7,FThomas' Cycling Club podcast, the 71-
OL,8,Fyear-old was asked whether he would
OL,9,Ftry and sign England star Bellingham.
OL,11,FHe replied: "He is a great footballer.
OL,12,FIt's not where our focus is, the
OL,13,Fsolution isn't spending a lot of money
OL,14,Fon a couple of great players. They
OL,15,Fhave done that, if you look at the
OL,16,Flast 10 years, they have spent a lot
OL,17,Fof money on a couple of great players.
