OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe: 'I would rather
OL,4,Csign the next Mbappe than buy success'
OL,6,F"The first thing we need to do is get
OL,7,Fthe right people in the right boxes
OL,8,Fwho are managing and organising the
OL,9,Fclub.
OL,11,F"And make sure we get recruitment
OL,12,Fright, it is such a vital part of
OL,13,Ffootball today."
OL,15,FLater in the podcast he was given a
OL,16,Fchoice of signing Mbappe for United or
OL,17,Fcyclist Tadej Pogacar for his Ineos
OL,18,Fteam and he said: "I would rather sign
OL,19,Fthe next Mbappe rather than spend a
OL,20,Ffortune buying success.
