OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe: 'I would rather
OL,4,Csign the next Mbappe than buy success'
OL,6,F"It's not that clever buying Mbappe.
OL,7,FAnyone could figure that one out. More
OL,8,Fchallenging is to find the next Mbappe
OL,9,For next Bellingham or next Roy Keane."
OL,11,FRadcliffe is working with his long-
OL,12,Fterm right-hand man Dave Brailsford at
OL,13,FUnited, with Omar Berrada incoming as
OL,14,Fchief executive.
OL,16,FAnd he said it would be a "longer
OL,17,Froad" to make United great again.
