OL,6,F"The two people who are most focused
OL,7,Fon it would be Dave and myself, in
OL,8,Fterms of how we resolve it all," he
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,F"We've now got Omar Berrada of course,
OL,12,Four new CEO from Manchester City, who
OL,13,Fis still on gardening leave at the
OL,14,Fmoment, he'll be a big part of it. But
OL,15,Fit's Dave and myself really.
