OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe: 'I would rather
OL,4,Csign the next Mbappe than buy success'
OL,6,F"You have to believe with Manchester
OL,7,FUnited, if we get all the details
OL,8,Fright, all the right people in the
OL,9,Fright boxes, doing the right things in
OL,10,Fthe right environment, that sporting
OL,11,Felite environment that the results
OL,12,Fwill drop out the bottom.
OL,14,F"Those things are not right at
OL,15,FManchester United today as we've said
OL,16,Fvery clearly."It's not a light switch,
OL,17,Fit's a much longer road to travel
OL,18,Fbecause there's so many aspects to it."
